data.description: Fresh n' neat 3/3/2 move in ready home located conveniently close to the military bases, shopping, and schools. This well-maintained 2-story with finished basement. Brand new interior paint and updated kitchen with new kitchen cabinets and refinished stone countertops. Three bedrooms with a full adjoining bathroom and desk nook on upper level. Spacious living room with vaulted ceiling and gas fireplace on main level. Easy to entertain with dining/kitchen combo with walkout to 16x7 back stamped concrete patio and fully fenced backyard. The basement features a family room, bonus room that could be used as 4th bedroom, 3/4 bath, and the laundry area. New furnace and central A/C in 2018, New roof and exterior paint in 2020, radon mitigation system and mountain views.
